;wxfrom=19" data-nickname="老万故事会" data-alias="laowangushihui" data-signature="文艺大叔老万，中科大学士，耶鲁博士，在谷歌做程序员十多年，智商配置一般，主频较低，小内存患者。文化程度较高，可以轻松阅读《知音》和《故事会》。偶尔写几个字，作点小曲，为您讲述他在IT届摸爬滚打的生活感悟和故事。不求有用，但求有趣。" data-origin_num="214" data-isban="0" data-biz_account_status="0" data-weuitheme="light" data-from="2"></mp-common-profile></p><p style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18.530001px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.59296px;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-size-adjust: inherit;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;"><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 17px;">本公众号不开赞赏不放广告。如果喜欢这篇文章，欢迎评论、转发、点“在看”。谢谢大家🙏</span></p></div></div></div></div><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p>]]></summary>
